    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Groups</strong> link [1], then click the name of the group [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_files" data-step-uuid="8560de64-3abf-45c7-9ca1-963e85ecaf3c">
    <h2 id="open_files" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Files</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/764/234/original/0211f494-7ae2-449b-a83d-8a895804960c.png" srcset="" alt="Open Files" height="231" width="173">
  </div>
 
